        <item>
            <title>【评测】Sky X Studio《忍者战士飞影》，武装丰富 + 大比例 + 高可动性</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/07/sky-x-studiotobikage/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sky-x-studiotobikage</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/07/sky-x-studiotobikage/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 07 Dec 2024 03:56:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1279785</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>愈来愈多厂方推出怀旧机械人动画的超合金 Figure，真的太好了，今次要开箱的是 39 年前的机械人动画《忍者战士飞影》中的飞影，但想不到一向都细细只的飞影，今次厂方会用大比例制作，实物是这么的大只。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC6501" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54188218504/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54188218504_feb53529fb_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6501" width="1024" height="618" /></a>▲可见飞影都真系几大只</p><p>1985 年的《忍者战士飞影》，不知大家还记不记得呢，作为一部无人驾驶的机械人 (前期)，有超强的战力，总会在主角们不够打时就会出场助阵 (出场时就会播放飞影专用 BGM)，好像开无双那样，战局就会逆转；还记得当年每集最期待的就是与黑狮子、凤雷鹰、爆龙其中之一合体，爆龙的大绝最有霸气。不过后期由阿祖驾驶飞影后，感觉像是被弱化了似的&#8230;&#8230;</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_48858"  width="590" height="443"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="443" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vLse-ehXuis?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_94049"  width="590" height="443"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="443" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/MNx5FP_nZx0?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>《忍者战士飞影》亦有在好几部机战作品登场，《机战 UX》，《机战 Impact》中都可说是主力的机体 (后期由阿祖驾驶后)，游戏前期阶段，不可操纵的飞影可说是经验值+金钱的小偷，小编对它又爱又恨。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279797" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ai4kuxsuperrobotwaru-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ai4kuxsuperrobotwaru-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ai4kuxsuperrobotwaru-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《机战 UX》的飞影</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ai4kuxsuperrobotwaru-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ai4kuxsuperrobotwaru-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/ai4kuxsuperrobotwaru.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《机战 UX》飞影的必杀分身攻击</p><h2>涂装细腻质感十足</h2><p>说了那么多回忆后，要说回正题了，香港厂方 Sky X Studio 推出的《忍者战士飞影》合金 Figure，作品不但忠实还原了动画中的经典形象，更在机体的细节、可动性以及丰富的武装方面，作出了很出色的表现。飞影整体色调饱和度高，有强烈的金属质感，细节部分也处理得非常细腻，例如身上的纹路都清晰可见，而眼睛部分本身已是作金色涂装，亦有 LED 发光效果，双眼的黄光是非常的光亮的，著灯后非常有神。除了关节部份外，飞影部分部件也采用了合金材质，增加重量手感也提升了耐用性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279804" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6212-528x580.jpg" alt="" width="528" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6212-528x580.jpg 528w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6212-scaled.jpg 819w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 528px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲很有型的包装盒</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279806" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6219-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6219-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6219-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全彩印刷说明书</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279805" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6218-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6218-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6218-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲说明书主要是讲解武器的装设情况</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279807" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6220-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6220-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6220-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲开箱后的主体板件</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279808" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6361-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6361-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6361-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另一板的武器配件</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279812" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6234-694x443.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="443" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6234-694x443.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6234-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲头盖采用磁吸，LED 灯入电位情况</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC6377" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54188217649/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54188217649_bb8b228cf1_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6377" width="1024" height="930" /></a> ▲眼睛的 LED 灯效是非常光，很有神。</p><p><a title="_DSC6227" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54188376735/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54188376735_d433574733_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6227" width="673" height="1024" /></a><br /><a title="_DSC6229" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54187933921/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54187933921_262797001d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6229" width="721" height="1024" /></a></p><h2>可动性高造型掌丰富</h2><p>飞影的可动性就有如动画一样，都是非常高可动灵活，它虽然大大只，实际上肢体可摆出很多动作，全身各处关节均采用了球形关节设计，确保了各个部位的灵活度。肩部、肘部、手腕等部位的可动范围较大，可以摆出各种动态姿势，腰部关节的设计也非常巧妙，能够实现大幅度的弯曲，让飞影的动作更加灵活。特别值得一提的是，小腿部分设计有连动装甲，当小腿弯曲时，装甲会随之开合，增加动态效果及细节；提供的造型手掌也非常丰富，大大提高了飞影的可玩性。值得一提的是头部的忍者帽末端是采用银色软胶制作，方便头部作任何方位的摆动时都不会受到阻碍，这个贴心的设计相当不错。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279809" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6230-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6230-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6230-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲忍者帽末端是用软胶制，头部如何摆动都不会有阻碍</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279811" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6233-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6233-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6233-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲头部可以 360 度转动</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279813" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6494-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6494-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6494-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲大腿的连动式关节，会见到内藏机械结构，以及可动情况</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279814" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6495-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6495-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6495-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲手臂的可动性情况</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279818" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6500-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6500-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6500-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲肩膊关节可拉出，提升可动性</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279815" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6496-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6496-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6496-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲前后裙甲可拉起，方便大腿作出大幅度动作</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279816" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6497-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6497-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6497-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲腰部的可动性</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279817" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6498-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6498-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/dsc6498-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> ▲腰部的可动性</p><p><a title="_DSC6375" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54188201663/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54188201663_d2fe57750c_b.jpg" alt="_DSC6375" width="642" height="1024" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲平衡度不错，摆出这样的 Pose 也不需用支架</p><h2>超丰富的武器配件</h2><p>飞影配备了多种武器配件，忍者刀、手里剑、星形光线炮、十字弩都有，充分还原了动画中飞影武器的多样性，而武器配件的细节刻画也非常精致，提升了整体质感和真实感。此外，武器配件与模型本体的结合设计合理，配合飞影的高可动性，能够摆出多种招牌战斗 Pose，对于作者 Fans 的小编而言，真系回忆都返晒来呀！</p><p><a title="_DSC6384" href="https://www.flickr.com/ph